Q: Allow the host to use the hostname google to reach www.google.com,
   and the hostname redhat to reach www.redhat.com.

1- Get the IP addresses of google.com and redhat.com

2- Open the /etc/hosts file:

sudo vi /etc/hosts

3- Add the following lines:

<IP address of google.com> google
<IP adress of redhat.com>  redhat
